{"tid":971186,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有生之年啊，IU X 李孝利 X 李尚順在濟州島合唱《孝利家民宿》裡的創作曲！","createTime":"2019-01-06T12:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T19:11:24.000Z","uid":34643,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"93c9e48729e895f5bc05fe071ef857a9e09dab71","tid":971186,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_cf579af3512ad2b16428f12afefb0ee7/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-01-06/112852-694027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_cf579af3512ad2b16428f12afefb0ee7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-01-06%2F112852-694027.jpg&h=eefefff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還記得IU和李孝利夫婦在《孝利家民宿》一起創作的歌嗎？<br />\n<br />\nIU在5日舉辦了亞巡的濟州島場，請來的嘉賓正是曾一起拍過《孝利家民宿》第一季綜藝的李孝利&amp;李尚順夫婦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ySuE37LqXDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DySuE37LqXDM&d=keks8wIK6uKY2hr1SzdLk5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=6dfb1d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ySuE37LqXDM</a><br />\n<br />\n三人合唱的歌曲也更加意義深刻，因為合唱的《孝利X知恩頌》是在《孝利家民宿》拍攝期間有感而發，共同創作出來的。 歌曲第一小節的靈感是李孝利從IU身上感受到的情感，第二小節則是IU從李孝利身上感受到的情感，是加入了兩人的聲音和李尚順的吉他演奏而完成的歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_699701f66d6b156503ab1d4f368bd6a8/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-01-06/112852-694025.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_699701f66d6b156503ab1d4f368bd6a8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-01-06%2F112852-694025.jpg&h=1a49a2b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_23f5951ea8ed4073e6bfd5296c109ef2/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-01-06/112852-694023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_23f5951ea8ed4073e6bfd5296c109ef2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-01-06%2F112852-694023.jpg&h=337555f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在三人舞台開始之前的談話環節，李孝利說因為是IU拜託的，所以不得不來了。 IU說：「這次是巡演的第10場，都是請了熟人來當嘉賓，這次是家人來了的感覺。 」李孝利繼續介紹到這首合唱歌的正式歌名是《她（그년는）》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nGRqc67YCns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnGRqc67YCns&d=keks8wIK6uKY2hr1SzdLk5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=8c2e15de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nGRqc67YCns</a><br />\n<br />\n沒想到在有生之年能看到這首歌的現場版，李孝利的低音和IU的低音巧妙融合，配上李尚順的吉他配樂，仿佛夢回2017年《孝利家民宿》播出的時期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RD3wjz7zfeI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRD3wjz7zfeI&d=keks8wIK6uKY2hr1SzdLk5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=7c9c0886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RD3wjz7zfeI</a><br />\n<br />\n李孝利夫婦搬家了，這次可能是專程去濟州島給IU當嘉賓，《孝利家民宿》出演者們的友情延續至今。"},{"pid":"81fd5f3b225f668f808c14feaced2e3fbcdb9f8e","tid":971186,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b65ca05a70a15eaa01c81ef336276ec7de622ebb","tid":971186,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"老婆唱歌好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584d75eb20e3a58010af50b4afb0523d060df9e8","tid":971186,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:37:35.000Z","msg":"係唔係個節目搞到佢地要搬屋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937f8c87aa7075e54ebb3d33b99fa69629da189d","tid":971186,"uid":170269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"584d75eb20e3a58010af50b4afb0523d060df9e8","tid":971186,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:37:35.000Z","msg":"係唔係個節目搞到佢地要搬屋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"個節目引晒啲冇腦嘅人上去佢哋嗰度"},{"pid":"af00575454e9487cbbf7b00b861fec6834d4